channel.title: Paulina Highway on Roadsign Pictures
channel.description: Recent content in Paulina Highway on Roadsign Pictures

item.title: End OR-380 West at US-26
item.description: End OR-380 West at US-26 in Prineville. Use US-26 east for Mitchell and John Day; US-26 west for Prineville and Redmond (via OR-126).

item.title: Pine Creek Road at OR-380
item.description: Pine Creek Road at OR-380. Turn left for OR-380 west to Post; right for OR-380 east to Paulina.

item.title: OR-380 West - Distance Marker
item.description: Distance marker on OR-380 west. Distance to Post and Prineville. This is the first OR-380 shield on OR-380 westbound.

item.title: Being OR-380 West - Paulina
item.description: Entering Paulina Oregon at the beginning of OR-380 West.
